      <title>消息人士稱，歐盟網路安全標籤投票延至五月</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/cybersecurity/vote-eu-cybersecurity-label-delayed-may-sources-say-2024-04-16/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士週二表示，國家網路安全專家已擱置對歐盟網路安全標籤草案的投票，該標籤允許亞馬遜、Alphabet 旗下谷歌和微軟在 5 月之前競標高度敏感的歐盟雲端運算合約。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/cybersecurity/vote-eu-cybersecurity-label-delayed-may-sources-say-2024-04-16/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 16:56:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
